          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Compiler's comment, May 2012: Emulsion technique is",
                "very good for detecting fission events or photostars.",
                "Certain fission products like gamma-rays could escape",
                "detection, however, the fission fragments and their",
